jmatrix

Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmatrix.Matrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public final class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    The Matrix class represents immutable numerical matrices, an m x n array of double values. This implementation is currently not thread-safe.
